docs {
  # Create Listing
  
  Creates a new sublet listing.
  
  ## Body Parameters
  - `ownerId` (required) - ID of the user creating the listing
  - `title` (required) - Listing title
  - `price` (required) - Monthly rent in dollars
  - `availableDate` (required) - When available, ISO date
  - `location` (required) - Address or neighborhood
  - `type` (required) - "studio" | "1br" | "2br" | "room"
  - `distanceTo` (optional) - Distance info, e.g. "10 mins to campus"
  - `amenities` (optional) - Array of amenity strings
  - `images` (optional) - Array of image URLs
  - `description` (optional) - Detailed description
}
